    relatedSlugs: ['jelly-truck', 'love-calculator', 'love-tester'],
    excerpt: 'This time-based mechanic completely changes how firefights feel.',
    content: `<p><strong>Time Shooter 3</strong> is an action-packed first-person shooting game that puts a unique twist on combat by controlling time itself. Unlike traditional shooters where everything moves at full speed, this game only moves when you move. The moment you stop, time slows almost to a complete halt, allowing you to plan every move carefully and react with precision.</p>

<p>This time-based mechanic completely changes how firefights feel. Bullets hang in the air, enemies freeze mid-action, and every step you take becomes a tactical decision. Instead of relying on fast reflexes alone, Time Shooter 3 rewards awareness, positioning, and smart movement. Each encounter feels more like a puzzle than a typical gunfight.</p>

<p>The game features a clean, minimalist visual style that keeps the focus on gameplay. Environments are simple but effective, making enemies and projectiles easy to track. This clarity is important, especially when navigating slow-motion moments where timing and accuracy matter most.</p>

<p>What makes Time Shooter 3 so engaging is how satisfying it feels when everything comes together. Dodging bullets at the last second, lining up perfect shots, and clearing a room without taking damage feels incredibly rewarding. The mix of strategy and action keeps the experience fresh and encourages players to improve with every attempt.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">How to Play Time Shooter 3</h2>

<p>Playing Time Shooter 3 is easy to understand, but mastering it takes practice. You move using standard controls, and time progresses only when you move your character. Standing still allows you to observe enemy positions, incoming bullets, and available weapons without pressure.</p>

<p>Movement is the key to success. Taking small, controlled steps lets you manage time effectively while staying aware of your surroundings. Rushing forward carelessly can cause time to speed up too quickly, making it harder to dodge attacks or react to sudden threats.</p>

<p>Weapons are scattered throughout the levels, and choosing the right one for each situation can make a big difference. You can pick up guns, throw weapons at enemies, or use objects in the environment to your advantage. Experimenting with different approaches adds variety to each playthrough.</p>

<p>To progress, you must eliminate all enemies in each area without getting hit. This often requires patience, careful positioning, and creative thinking. Time Shooter 3 rewards players who stay calm, plan ahead, and use the slow-motion mechanics wisely, making every victory feel earned.</p>
<div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;'>

</div>
<!-- CONTENT END 1 -->`,
